Package edu.uiuc.ncsa.security.oauth_1_0a

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OAuthConstants
    Constants that are used for OAuth.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OAuthHTTPSClientPool
    Wraps an HTTPS client, not an OAuth one, but this is needed since the Java implementation of OAuth 1 will leak these unless there is a pool.
    OAuthTokenForge
    A forge for OAuth 1.0a tokens following semantics of the delelgation framework.
    OAuthUtilities
    Utilities for OAuth.
